  <div id="text-content_cdd7ba8e-6f72-48de-8d28-4912943476a1" class="text-block-content">
    <p>By default, an icon displays next to all unread discussion replies. As you scroll down the page, that icon will be removed from each reply.</p>
<p>You can tell Canvas not to automatically mark all your posts as read in your <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-change-discussion-settings-to-manually-mark-discussion/ta-p/1287" target="_blank">Discussion settings</a>. </p>
<p>If the steps in this lesson do not match what is displayed in your course, learn how to <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-mark-discussions-replies-as-read-or-unread-in/ta-p/469512" target="_blank">mark discussion replies as read or unread in the Discussions Redesign interface</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> If a reply's state is manually changed, the post will not change states unless you manually change it again.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_discussions" data-step-uuid="929e67e8-d371-41ea-b1b2-3a506b7271a5">
    <h2 id="open_discussions" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Discussions</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/467/756/original/48bad6be-98c5-4225-ab4c-47c72442f93b.png" srcset="" alt="Open Discussions" height="258" width="175">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_46043505-9410-4da8-a35e-a76571b6e0ad" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Discussions</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_discussion" data-step-uuid="ce2f87d8-1004-47ed-9553-9b6f12190645">
    <h2 id="open_discussion" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Discussion</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/467/758/original/8debfe11-6708-4a4e-a217-1f2a1d1ca065.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/467/758/medium/8debfe11-6708-4a4e-a217-1f2a1d1ca065.png" srcset="" alt="Open Discussion" height="223" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_9610c449-3c3c-4608-8927-19cc0a51d995" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the discussion you want to view. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view_posts" data-step-uuid="466bb5bc-c571-46a2-8521-90b2b3b332cf">
    <h2 id="view_posts" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Posts</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/652/495/original/3884d47a-1908-4a3f-9f99-ab5a2aaed194.png" srcset="" alt="View Posts" height="514" width="724">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_b11baa68-f7ec-47d5-971b-ff437b5ed62c" class="text-block-content">
    <p>The Unread icon indicates replies that have not been read [1].</p>
<p>If the Unread icon does not display, it means the post has been read or marked as read [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="mark_post_as_unread" data-step-uuid="f337e990-53c8-4edf-924d-ccddcf1c8e63">
    <h2 id="mark_post_as_unread" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Mark Post as Unread</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/695/976/original/30260b9f-f66f-4fa1-9f54-da9b0914430d.png" srcset="" alt="Mark Post as Unread" height="293" width="650">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_07d07257-ff41-44b7-8254-477fc04d1e30" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To mark a reply as unread, click the <strong>Options</strong> icon next to the reply [1] and click the <strong>Mark as Unread</strong> link [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="verify_post_as_unread" data-step-uuid="c6f39376-6621-4497-8635-96fe96d4a9da">
    <h3 id="verify_post_as_unread" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Verify Post as Unread </h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/652/499/original/3dbd7cd8-0173-4029-9c90-7d4c4524b11b.png" srcset="" alt="Verify Post as Unread " height="173" width="216">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_d173ed80-7e35-4e28-8051-9b18686eaf25" class="text-block-content">
    <p>View the <strong>Unread</strong> icon, which indicates the reply is marked as unread. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="mark_post_as_read" data-step-uuid="a3fc44a3-a763-4881-8982-ca2db47a8957">
    <h2 id="mark_post_as_read" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Mark Post as Read</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/695/979/original/7a7ce82c-62dd-4f02-a7ed-54c07d0e9dfb.png" srcset="" alt="Mark Post as Read" height="292" width="673">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_7831f812-a1d6-44ff-b971-624c2032cf54" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To change an unread reply to read, click the <strong>Options</strong> icon next to the reply [1] and click the <strong>Mark as Read</strong> link [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="verify_post_as_read" data-step-uuid="175c4797-4f64-4d5d-b8c0-34033f9d2288">
    <h3 id="verify_post_as_read" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Verify Post as Read</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/652/503/original/d860354d-1032-43e9-9267-9e8ba4ae3f77.png" srcset="" alt="Verify Post as Read" height="180" width="218">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_ecf10272-a11a-4af0-bbf8-f7fbce29c5a8" class="text-block-content">
    <p>View the post marked as read. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_2ce98b9c-5c8f-4810-b1f0-90928093641f" class="text-block-content">
    <p><strong>Note:</strong> If a reply's state is manually changed, the post will not change states unless you manually change it again.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
